Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.32,0:00:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness!\NThat couldn't be a better match!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your skin tone pairs with it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot wait to see you\Nwearing it around town.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a cherry blossom pink kimono\Njust like my mother's.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a beautiful color on her.\NWouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.17,0:00:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Lord Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.26,0:00:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can accept these kimonos.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There are just so many,\Nand they're so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept them as a thank you\Nfor your hair tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, alright then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.02,0:00:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This material was chosen just for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,by none other than Mr. Kudo himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so very happy for you, Miss Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm very grateful for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,MY HAPPY MARRIAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}EPISODE 5 RIPPLES
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Who would have thought\Nshe could win over Kudo of all people?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, old man.\NIf that's a joke, I'm not laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.14,0:02:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This concerns your sister.\NWhy would I ever make light of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the least bit curious\Nabout how she's doing over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The man at the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:02:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that means he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:03:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,As that photo shows...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...Miyo is doing exceptionally well\Nwith Kiyoka Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're telling me that\Nthat's Kiyoka Kudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Never would've thought\Nthat timid little Miyo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,would end up as Kudo's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, it's a real inconvenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- I had planned for Miyo...\N-{\i1}I won't allow it!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- ...to marry Kazushi.\N-{\i1}I won't! I won't! I won't!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Shinichi didn't want you,\Nhis precious younger daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to marry someone with\Nsuch a notorious reputation like Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I just go straight\Nto my father and make a request?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wanting my help with this, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My Father loves to spoil me,\Nso he'd never say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Foolish little girl.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's saving me all the trouble\Nby doing it herself.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks to Lord Kudo and Mr. Godo,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was finally able to reunite with Hana.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I decided to make them dinner{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and invited Mr. Godo\Nto come share a meal at our home.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't thank them enough\Nbut it's a start.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I get to see Miss Miyo again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you don't get too carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your night patrol starts tomorrow,\Ndoesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what she'd cook tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be delicious either way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act too familiar with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, was that jealousy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that was not jealousy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It was merely a violent impulse\Nthat overtook me for a brief moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}In other words, it was jealousy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, n-nothing, it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here, so get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! There's no need to get so violent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it or I will tell Miss Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You could disappear right now\Nand I'd be fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm laughing, Commander, joke's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Lord Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why hello Miss Miyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to our home, Mr. Godo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you just especially stunning today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, My Lord, is there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so... so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This kimono suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I'm not even here. I can just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? My sincerest apologies, Mr. Godo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you'll just follow me this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does my sister look\Nso much happier than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll never get away with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.12,0:06:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm! This is the best thing\NI've eaten in a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please have as much food as you care to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What a dream your life must be
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to have home cooked meals\Nfrom Miss Miyo every single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so jealous of you, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me try this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- So, Mr. Godo...\N- Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...might I now pour you a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,for all of your help the other day\Nthat I reunited with Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, all I did was give her a ride\Nto the house, and that was it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, precious hours\Nfrom your life were spent
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,helping someone you didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I am deeply indebted to you for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never had anyone say\Nsuch kind things like that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My Commander's such a stick in the mud.\NDump him and marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Godo! You rat bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, it was only joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, no! Mr. Godo...\N- Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your request, but you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be with Lord Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you really didn't need\Nto take that so seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you have\Nsome human qualities, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I just hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you didn't hear anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! I love you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What a menace! Of course he overdid it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,right when things are\Ngetting busy at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that bad? Did I cause you trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But you did surprise me when you wanted\Nto host a dinner with Godo as our guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do you think tonight's dinner went?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did everything turn out\Nthe way that you wanted it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was all because of you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that I was able\Nto show my gratitude this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing more to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You should forget about Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:08:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I when it's clear
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm obviously better suited\Nfor the Kudos?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- I said no.\N- But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?\NWhy aren't you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kaya, if your boredom is so intense,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}then why don't you go be good\Nand practice homemaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are nothing\Nlike that "thing".{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You must be better\Nthan your sister in every way.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, Koji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. It's pretty late,\Nis something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You know, I was thinking, Koji...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you prefer\Nto be engaged to my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Make it stop!\N- Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna see your face again
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,until you've reflected\Non what you've done today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:10:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Remnants of an ability?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the barrier\Naround the house wasn't broken...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You cried out, so I was concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? Were you having a nightmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't force yourself to remember, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,if you sense anything wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,please don't hesitate\Nto tell me right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Miyo, whatever you're facing,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}wherever you go, you are never alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I understand, Lord Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wouldn't you prefer\Nto be engaged to my sister?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I already talked to your father,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}and he's more than willing\Nto help us with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So of course, you're going\Nto help us too, aren't you, Koji?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya and my father?\NWhat are they planning to do to Miyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There, ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he will be delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Young Master can get\Ntoo overwhelmed with his duties at work
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and doesn't care to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wager he's famished around now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope this won't trouble him
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,for us to be dropping in on him\Nwhile he's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You needn't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You should get dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We can pack up and leave\Nas soon as you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,On my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,For today, why don't you carry\Nthis pouch into town instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master had it made for you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to match the kimono\Nyou're wearing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What a great chance to use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the Young Master will get to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect! Great idea! Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We should get going when you're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're hoping to make it there\Nby lunchtime, we might want to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.19,0:13:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, it will arrive right on time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, may I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.54,0:14:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello there, Koji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya. What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to exchange fiancés\Nwith my elder sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hear how foolish you sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Only to your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really going to lie to me\Nand say you don't love my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Your father already said\Nhe wasn't going to allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If the head of the family doesn't approve,\Nthis won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But what if my sister is\Nthe one who agrees to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.95,0:14:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You'll understand it all in time.\NJust trust me for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Watch and it will all make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo. Yurie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are the two of you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon. I know this is a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly hope\Nwe aren't disrupting your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.94,0:15:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried you might not be\Ntaking any time for a break or a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So I brought a lunch for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I... Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That was, um, quite thoughtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You walked all the way here\Nin the sun, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't the two of you\Ntake a rest inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We're alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the offer but I don't want\Nto take any more of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be on our way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, please excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo, wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,do you have the amulet with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I do. I have it right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember to keep it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:16:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have driven you back to the house,\Nbut we're a bit occupied here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We will be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that\Nyou're incredibly busy with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.03,0:16:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no trouble at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care and get back home safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks as if\Nthe Young Master was embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.42,0:16:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Miss Miyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not... Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The amulet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I must've forgotten it at home.\NIt's not in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because\NI was rushing you out today, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I should've double checked\Nbefore we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And right after I promised him\Nand saying I'd always have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then, Miss Miyo,\Nwe must return to the house at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How could I? I really am the worst.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lord Kudo gave me\Na precious amulet, and I forgot it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I got so excited about the new pouch{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I left it behind.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Yurie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo! Miss Miyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Yurie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Miss Miyo! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.53,0:17:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Miss Miyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two\Nplanning on doing with Miyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We're going to have Sister withdraw
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}from the marriage arrangements\Nwith the head of the Kudos,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That should be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't afford to stay silent\Non such an important family matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then, I'll be waiting\Nat the Saimori house for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to secure Miyo, Koji.\NWe have no choice here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't Miyo deserve happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This complication affects\Nboth our families.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's convenient Miyo's situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If she were less isolated\Nor treated with dignity,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,things would be more difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You have the privilege\Nof not needing to care.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But I have to do anything within my power\Nto see that our lineage will thrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the head of the Tatsuishi family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew and you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,For all these years,\Nyou knew that Miyo was getting abused
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and being treated as a servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You never lent her a hand
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}and it was all for your benefit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Do you really want\Nto pit your gift against mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you think you're going to say,\Nyou can save it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Listen, boy. That is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I won't let you do anything\Nto Miyo ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.01,0:19:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, I didn't expect your abilities\Nto be this strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me! Please stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Are you an imbecile?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You think because you're angry,\Nyour abilities would overpower mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A novice can't possibly take on\Na lifetime of training.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If all I'll get from you is\Nresistance to this,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,then stay there until it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:19:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Koji.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.64,0:20:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you want something in life,\Nyou have to decide how to get it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Put thought into how to make things happen\Nor you'll always be second-rate.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over. I'm a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasting even more of your time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Or were you planning\Nto stare at the floor all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I have failed her so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't even win against Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep saying\NI'll protect her, but I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, does that mean you're done?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When things are complicated,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes it's better\Nto keep your nose out of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.73,0:20:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Curious. Why even try to battle with Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,if you still were planning\Nto sit around here when you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Go wash your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there's someone who needs you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miyo.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't give up.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to save her.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so sorry, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo was kidnapped right off the street?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one who was with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry! I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the amulet she has?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was with her, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She realized she didn't have it\Njust after we had left you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.07,0:21:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know who's behind this.\NThere's no question about it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.91,0:21:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But where is she?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! This area is off-limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to see Mr. Kudo right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.79,0:21:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, out of everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be the last person\Nto ask this of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, you have to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't, I can't save Miyo without you!
